{"serial": "80001", "department_serial": 76, "code": "SA5002", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to the IPCC assessment reports", "ch": "IPCC報告導讀"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Chien, Hwa", "Dong, Jia-Jyun", "Li, Ming-Hsu", "Ou-Yang, Chang-Feng", "Wang, Sheng-Hsiang", "Ni, Chuen-Fa"], "ch": ["錢樺", "董家鈞", "李明旭", "歐陽長風", "王聖翔", "倪春發"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "S", "room": "135"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "永續與綠能科技研究學院", "en": "Graduate College of Sustainability and Green Energy"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 24, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在幫助學生深入理解並解讀《政府間氣候變化專門委員會（IPCC）》報告，掌握其核心內容和科學依據，並能夠將報告中的關鍵資訊應用於政策制定、社會行動及日常生活中。具體課程目標包括：\n\n理解IPCC報告的結構與內容、掌握氣候變化的科學基礎、分析氣候變化的社會、了解減緩與適應策略、提升氣候行動的能力、促進批判性思維與討論、培養跨學科合作精神…本課程適合所有對氣候變化有興趣的學者、政策制定者、環保工作者及任何希望了解氣候變化科學和應對策略的社會大眾。", "en": "This course aims to help students gain a deep understanding of and interpret the reports of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change (IPCC), grasp their core content and scientific basis, and apply key information from the reports to policy-making, social action, and daily life. Specific course objectives include:\n\nUnderstanding the structure and content of the IPCC reports\nMastering the scientific foundations of climate change\nAnalyzing the social, economic, and environmental impacts of climate change\nUnderstanding mitigation and adaptation strategies\nEnhancing the ability to take climate action\nPromoting critical thinking and discussion\nFostering interdisciplinary collaboration\nThis course is suitable for scholars, policymakers, environmental professionals, and anyone interested in understanding climate change science and response strategies."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程前四周預計邀請相關專家做主題演講，其餘由6位老師帶領學生做不同主題之分組報告，每組報告2次。\n第一週\n主題：IPCC報告導論與課程概述\n第二週\n主題：氣候科學與氣候變遷\n第三週\n主題：氣候變遷衝擊與調適\n第四週\n主題：氣候變遷的國際合作", "en": "The first four weeks of this course are expected to feature guest lectures by relevant experts on specific topics. The remaining sessions will be led by six instructors, guiding students through group presentations on different topics, with each group presenting twice.\nWeek 1\nTopic: Introduction to the IPCC Reports and Course Overview\nWeek 2\nTopic: Climate Science and Climate Change\nWeek 3\nTopic: Impacts of Climate Change and Adaptation\nWeek 4\nTopic: International Cooperation on Climate Change"}, "textbook": {"ch": "AR6_WGI\nAR6_WGII", "en": "AR6_WGI\nAR6_WGII"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "100%", "en": "100%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "課堂報告100％", "en": "Group report 100％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "請與老師聯繫", "en": "Please email to the teacher"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "map": {"ch": [], "en": []}, "assignCriteria": {"ch": ["學院:限永續與綠能科技研究學院。"], "en": ["Faculty:College of Graduate College of Sustainability and Green Energy only."]}, "preselecStu": 0, "stuGender": {"male": 0, "Female": 0}, "stuGrade": {"doctor": {}, "master": {}, "bachelor": {}}, "stus": [{"serial": "1", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "永續去碳科技碩士學位學程", "grade": "1", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": false, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": false}, {"serial": "2", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "永續去碳科技碩士學位學程", "grade": "1", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": false, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": false}, {"serial": "3", "stunum": "11*******", "department": "永續綠能科技碩士學位學程", "grade": "1", "class": "*", "priority": "1", "isRequired": false, "isPreselected": false, "isManuallySelected": false, "isCodeSelected": fals